snippet.textDisplay: My niece is a Gemini....she’s clumsy af! She’s super gentle; literally when she was 3 years old to even now, she waves and says hello to everyone. She’s super extroverted and happy. She’s super sweet and she got bullied a lot because of it, well, also because she was well endowed in the...bust area. She had almost double D boobs at the age of 10, and girls got jealous and said she got breast implants. That hurts. But even with all of that, she’s super genuinely sweet and doesn’t hold grudges. She’s not a fighter anyways, she will literally tell a joke to lighten the mood and not get confrontational. Ginny, my niece I’m talking about, does love routine, but she does get bored sometimes. Ginny would wake up early in the morning: she said “if the sun is up, I am up.” That was from the age 4 to now. She always had soooo much energy. She used to talk fast, but went to speech therapy, because speech impediments run in my family, she had a slight lisp, that and she needed braces because her upper teeth/jaw was pushing on her upper lip, similar to Freddie Mercury’s problem when he was still alive. But ya, I don’t understand where people are getting at that Geminis are two faced and not gentle. I’ve met only the nice geminis. 😂🤷🏼‍♀️
